		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>78 Nassan St</placeName></p>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>N.Y.</placeName> <date>July 26&#47;66</date></p>
				<p><addressee>Rev. I Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Revd dear Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">I have just<lb/> rec&#39;d your Bibles. Didn&#39;t<lb/> fully understand the price.<lb/> Was it &#36;15 wholesale or retail&#63;<lb/> And is the Bible in sheets &#36;2.50 to<lb/> me&#8212; it was for my own use</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I send the circular&#44; which<lb/> has just been printed.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Saw <persName>Mr Peixotto</persName>. He will shortly<lb/> visit <placeName>Phila.</placeName> &#38; will speak with<lb/> you on the subject of the<lb/> College. It would be well to<lb/> reserve opinion&#44; until you<lb/> see him.</p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p>My brother explained to you<lb/> I presume the reason<lb/> of my not calling in<lb/> person <date>Monday</date> AM</p>
			<p rend="indent(10)">Truly Yours</p>
			<p rend="indent(10)"><persName role="author">M. J. Isaacs</persName>.</p>
				<p>We want to issue shortly<lb/> blanks for statistics.  Also<lb/> we should take some action<lb/> as to Publications. If you<lb/> have any suggestions please<lb/> communicate them.</p>
		</body>
